"1\" />',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(232,0,0,'The Spectrum of Educational Technology','text/html','http://apointofcontact.wordpress.com/2012/08/21/the-spectrum-of-educational-technology/','Distance Education;educational technology;learner autonomy;McLuhan;technology',NULL,NULL,17,NULL,NULL,NULL,31,'The body is a frontier between myself and everything else The spectrum of information communication, which I mentioned in my Vygotsky post and in another previous post, is a perspective on educational technology worth detailing a bit deeper. It&#8217;s probably a common concept, but I could best explain the idea as an x and y [...]<img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=apointofcontact.wordpress.com&#038;blog=9885639&#038;post=753&#038;subd=apointofcontact&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />',1347893163,NULL,NULL,'Glenyan','http://apointofcontact.wordpress.com','Tue, 21 Aug 2012 13:06:18 +0000',NULL,'A Point of Contact',NULL,'The body is a frontier between myself and everything else The spectrum of information communication, which I mentioned in my Vygotsky post and in another previous post, is a perspective on educational technology worth detailing a bit deeper. It&#8217;s probably a common concept, but I could best explain the idea as an x and y [...]<img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=apointofcontact.wordpress.com&#038;blog=9885639&#038;post=753&#038;subd=apointofcontact&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(233,0,0,'Military Flow in Asia','text/html','http://apointofcontact.wordpress.com/2012/08/20/military-flow-in-asia/','Life in Japan;China;japanese government;Senkaku',NULL,NULL,17,NULL,NULL,NULL,31,'I often run into simple reminders about how close this society is to being under military rule. This past weekend was the summer festival in our neighborhood. I was away and couldn&#8217;t attend and unfortunately, for everyone else here, it was rained out. They did prepare for the festival, and in doing so the people [...]<img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=apointofcontact.wordpress.com&#038;blog=9885639&#038;post=748&#038;subd=apointofcontact&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />',1347893163,NULL,NULL,'Glenyan','http://apointofcontact.wordpress.com','Mon, 20 Aug 2012 13:47:15 +0000',NULL,'A Point of Contact',NULL,'I often run into simple reminders about how close this society is to being under military rule. This past weekend was the summer festival in our neighborhood. I was away and couldn&#8217;t attend and unfortunately, for everyone else here, it was rained out. They did prepare for the festival, and in doing so the people [...]<img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=apointofcontact.wordpress.com&#038;blog=9885639&#038;post=748&#038;subd=apointofcontact&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(234,0,0,'Using Vygotsky to Understand Connectivism: Proximity and Duration','text/html','http://apointofcontact.wordpress.com/2012/08/08/using-vygotsky-to-understand-connectivism-proximity-and-duration/','Distance Education;connections;connectivism;constructivist theories;educational technology;educational theory;intention;McLuhan;potential vs actual;values on information;Vygotsky',NULL,NULL,17,NULL,NULL,NULL,31,'Vygotsky divides the idea of development into two developmental levels: a potential developmental level and a completed developmental level. Starting at the potential developmental level a learner can begin to complete a task with assistance; then at the completed developmental level the learner can complete the task autonomously. Between these two barriers is created a [...]<img alt=\"\" bo