kipedia.org/wiki/File:State_Library_of_New_South_Wales_8.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: clear:right;\"><img alt=\"State Library of New South Wales\" border=\"0\" class=\"zemanta-img-inserted\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/State_Library_of_New_South_Wales_8.jpg/300px-State_Library_of_New_South_Wales_8.jpg\" style=\"border: none; font-size: 0.8em;\" width=\"300\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption zemanta-img-attribution\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 300px;\">State Library of New South Wales (Photo credit: <a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:State_Library_of_New_South_Wales_8.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a>)</td></tr></tbody></table><a href=\"http://www.sl.nsw.gov.au/events/exhibitions/future.html#.T-1aJRJ5G9A.blogger\">Future exhibitions | State Library of New South Wales</a><br /><br />Exciting&amp;nbsp;<b></b><br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.sl.nsw.gov.au/events/exhibitions/index.html\">The current shows are good too.</a><br /> <a class=\"zemanta-pixie-a\" href=\"http://www.zemanta.com/?px\" title=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\"><img alt=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\" class=\"zemanta-pixie-img\" src=\"http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=255fd7f2-b1be-4327-a2e5-b26f1bc1dd39\" style=\"border: none; float: right;\" /></a><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-2979709674309988620?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(299,0,0,'The lecturer: yes, there are jobs out there for journalists | Crikey','text/html','http://notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com/2012/06/the-lecturer-yes-there-are-jobs-out.html','#blogjune',NULL,NULL,21,NULL,NULL,'2012-06-29 16:38:58',37,'<br />Another reason why high school students need access to social media in Australia as illustrated this article by:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.crikey.com.au/2012/06/29/the-lecturer-yes-there-are-jobs-out-there-for-journalists/\">Jenna Price</a><br />But what breaks my heart is the way in which young students, about to graduate, ask me if they will ever get work as journalists. My always truthful answer isâ€‰-â€‰it depends.<br /><br /><br />Are you doing the best kind of journalism you can do? Can you break the odd story? Can you deliver it across all media? Can you curate Twitter feeds? Can you do a decent photo gallery? Do you know how to use Twitter and Facebook for research and promotion of your own work? Do you know how to bill? Alan and Arianna will not be the only ones to make their money from online.<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.crikey.com.au/2012/06/29/the-lecturer-yes-there-are-jobs-out-there-for-journalists/#.T-1KGI-hq34.blogger\" style=\"background-color: white;\">The lecturer: yes, there are jobs out there for journalists | Crikey</a><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-6110905196354166793?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',1347893885,NULL,NULL,'markwashere','http://www.blogger.com/profile/16895029067006588081','2012-06-29T16:32:00.000+10:00',NULL,'something found or shared',NULL,'<br />Another reason why high school students need access to social media in Australia as illustrated this article by:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.crikey.com.au/2012/06/29/the-lecturer-yes-there-are-jobs-out-there-for-journalists/\">Jenna Price</a><br />But what breaks my heart is the way in which young students, about to graduate, ask me if they will ever get work as journalists. My always truthful answer isâ€‰-â€‰it depends.<br /><br /><br />Are you doing the best kind of journalism you can do? Can you break the odd story? Can you deliver it across all media? Can you curate Twitter feeds? Can you do a decent photo gallery? Do you know how to use Twitter and Facebook for research and promotion of your own work? Do you know how to bill? Alan and Arianna will not be the only ones to make their money from online.<br /><br /><a href=\"http://www.crikey.com.au/2012/06/29/the-lecturer-yes-there-are-jobs-out-there-for-journalists/#.T-1KGI-hq34.blogger\" style=\"background-color: white;\">The lecturer: yes, there are jobs out there for journalists | Crikey</a><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-6110905196354166793?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(300,0,0,'Book Week @ Taronga Video Conferences','text/html','http://notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com/2012/06/book-week-taronga-video-conferences.html',NULL,NULL,NULL,21,NULL,NULL,'2012-06-27 23:39:32',37,'<a href=\"http://darcymoore.net/2012/06/27/book-week-taronga-video-conferences/\">Book Week @ Taronga Video Conferences</a><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-8872855738855692005?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',1347893885,NULL,NULL,'markwashere','http://www.blogger.com/profile/16895029067006588081','2012-06-27T23:39:00.001+10:00',NULL,'something found or shared',NULL,'<a href=\"http://darcymoore.net/2012/06/27/book-week-taronga-video-conferences/\">Book Week @ Taronga Video Conferences</a><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-8872855738855692005?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(301,0,0,'3rd Biennale of Sydney (1979) | 18th Biennale of Sydney: all our relations','text/html','http://notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com/2012/06/3rd-biennale-of-sydney-1979-18th.html','Australia',NULL,NULL,21,NULL,NULL,'2012-06-27 16:56:18',37,'<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container zemanta-img\" style=\"float: right; margin-right: 1em; text-align: right;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:NSWAG.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: clear:right;\"><img alt=\"English: photo of the New South Wales Art Gallery\" border=\"0\" class=\"zemanta-img-inserted\" height=\"187\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d9/NSWAG.jpg/300px-NSWAG.jpg\" style=\"border: none; font-size: 0.8em;\" width=\"300\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption zemanta-img-attribution\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 300px;\">English: photo of the New South Wales Art Gallery (Photo credit: <a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:NSWAG.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a>)</td></tr></tbody></table><a href=\"http://www.biennaleofsydney.com.au/about/history/1979#.T-mFuaXj1Cc.blogger\">3rd Biennale of Sydney (1979) | 18th Biennale of Sydney: all our relations</a><br /><br />Yes Nick 1979 was one of the very best and memorable Biennale&apos;s for me ever! We had a great time sending up most of the exhibits I still smile thinking of us cheering the film loop of the guy with the penal <a class=\"zem_slink\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erection\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Erection\">erection</a> \"Marina Abramovic and Ulay and their remarkable performance work, and a film loop with them both naked â€“ Ulay with an erection\" with the <a class=\"zem_slink\" href=\"http://www.artgallery.nsw.gov.au/\" rel=\"homepage\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Art Gallery of New South Wales\">Art Gallery of NSW</a> guards trying to work out what to do about the us and deciding that it was too funny to interfere.<br />The placing in the full&amp;nbsp;<a class=\"zem_slink\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milk_bottle\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Milk bottle\">milk bottle</a> next to the dehydrated cow was classic as it stayed in the exhibit the whole show. Thanks for the memories Nick.<br /><br /><br /><a class=\"zemanta-pixie-a\" href=\"http://www.zemanta.com/?px\" title=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\"><img alt=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\" class=\"zemanta-pixie-img\" src=\"http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=fe2efb2d-3fd4-4a93-9bc7-a7f6d7d05f50\" style=\"border: none; float: right;\" /></a> <iframe src=\"http://www.smh.com.au/action/externalEmbeddedPlayer?id=d-2107u\" width=\"420\" height=\"236\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-5956888806842817348?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',1347893885,NULL,NULL,'markwashere','http://www.blogger.com/profile/16895029067006588081','2012-06-26T20:02:00.002+10:00',NULL,'something found or shared',NULL,'<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container zemanta-img\" style=\"float: right; margin-right: 1em; text-align: right;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:NSWAG.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: clear:right;\"><img alt=\"English: photo of the New South Wales Art Gallery\" border=\"0\" class=\"zemanta-img-inserted\" height=\"187\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d9/NSWAG.jpg/300px-NSWAG.jpg\" style=\"border: none; font-size: 0.8em;\" width=\"300\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption zemanta-img-attribution\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 300px;\">English: photo of the New South Wales Art Gallery (Photo credit: <a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:NSWAG.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a>)</td></tr></tbody></table><a href=\"http://www.biennaleofsydney.com.au/about/history/1979#.T-mFuaXj1Cc.blogger\">3rd Biennale of Sydney (1979) | 18th Biennale of Sydney: all our relations</a><br /><br />Yes Nick 1979 was one of the very best and memorable Biennale&apos;s for me ever! We had a great time sending up most of the exhibits I still smile thinking of us cheering the film loop of the guy with the penal <a class=\"zem_slink\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erection\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Erection\">erection</a> \"Marina Abramovic and Ulay and their remarkable performance work, and a film loop with them both naked â€“ Ulay with an erection\" with the <a class=\"zem_slink\" href=\"http://www.artgallery.nsw.gov.au/\" rel=\"homepage\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Art Gallery of New South Wales\">Art Gallery of NSW</a> guards trying to work out what to do about the us and deciding that it was too funny to interfere.<br />The placing in the full&amp;nbsp;<a class=\"zem_slink\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milk_bottle\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Milk bottle\">milk bottle</a> next to the dehydrated cow was classic as it stayed in the exhibit the whole show. Thanks for the memories Nick.<br /><br /><br /><a class=\"zemanta-pixie-a\" href=\"http://www.zemanta.com/?px\" title=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\"><img alt=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\" class=\"zemanta-pixie-img\" src=\"http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=fe2efb2d-3fd4-4a93-9bc7-a7f6d7d05f50\" style=\"border: none; float: right;\" /></a> <iframe src=\"http://www.smh.com.au/action/externalEmbeddedPlayer?id=d-2107u\" width=\"420\" height=\"236\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-5956888806842817348?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(302,0,0,'Another person who needs saving from extradition','text/html','http://notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com/2012/06/another-person-who-needs-saving-from.html','#blogjune',NULL,NULL,21,NULL,NULL,'2012-06-27 11:56:00',37,'<br />Richard O&apos;Dwyer is a 24 year old British student at Sheffield Hallam University in the UK.&amp;nbsp;<strong style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">He is facing extradition to the USA and up to ten years in prison</strong>, for creating a website â€“&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"http://tvshack.net/\" style=\"background-image: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font: inherit; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">TVShack.net</a>&amp;nbsp;â€“ which linked (similar to a search-engine) to places to watch TV and movies online.<br /><br /><br /><br /><h2>  <a href=\"http://www.change.org/petitions/ukhomeoffice-stop-the-extradition-of-richard-o-dwyer-to-the-usa-saverichard\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.change.org/petitions/ukhomeoffice-stop-the-extradition-of-richard-o-dwyer-to-the-usa-saverichard</a><br /><br /><br />- Jimmy Wales,&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page\" style=\"background-image: none; border: none; color: #004e75; cursor: pointer; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a>&amp;nbsp;founder</h2><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-5472110838919566878?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',1347893886,NULL,NULL,'markwashere','http://www.blogger.com/profile/16895029067006588081','2012-06-26T12:03:00.000+10:00',NULL,'something found or shared',NULL,'<br />Richard O&apos;Dwyer is a 24 year old British student at Sheffield Hallam University in the UK.&amp;nbsp;<strong style=\"border: 0px; font: inherit; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">He is facing extradition to the USA and up to ten years in prison</strong>, for creating a website â€“&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"http://tvshack.net/\" style=\"background-image: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font: inherit; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">TVShack.net</a>&amp;nbsp;â€“ which linked (similar to a search-engine) to places to watch TV and movies online.<br /><br /><br /><br /><h2>  <a href=\"http://www.change.org/petitions/ukhomeoffice-stop-the-extradition-of-richard-o-dwyer-to-the-usa-saverichard\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.change.org/petitions/ukhomeoffice-stop-the-extradition-of-richard-o-dwyer-to-the-usa-saverichard</a><br /><br /><br />- Jimmy Wales,&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page\" style=\"background-image: none; border: none; color: #004e75; cursor: pointer; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a>&amp;nbsp;founder</h2><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-5472110838919566878?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(303,0,0,'10 Reasons Why Twitter Is Great For Writers','text/html','http://notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com/2012/06/10-reasons-why-twitter-is-great-for.html','Social network',NULL,NULL,21,NULL,NULL,'2012-06-25 18:41:50',37,'Even writers think twitter is a helpful tool.<br /><br /><h2 style=\"color: #888888; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font: normal normal bold 1