ssing Bottom Points Signal Box on the L...\" border=\"0\" class=\"zemanta-img-inserted\" height=\"292\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/1072_passing_Bottom_Points_Signal_Box_on_the_Lithgow_Zig_Zag_railway_line.jpg/300px-1072_passing_Bottom_Points_Signal_Box_on_the_Lithgow_Zig_Zag_railway_line.jpg\" style=\"border: none; font-size: 0.8em;\" width=\"300\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption zemanta-img-attribution\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 300px;\">1072 passing Bottom Points Signal Box on the Lithgow Zig Zag railway line. (Photo credit: <a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:1072_passing_Bottom_Points_Signal_Box_on_the_Lithgow_Zig_Zag_railway_line.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a>)</td></tr></tbody></table><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container zemanta-img\" style=\"float: right; margin-right: 1em; text-align: right;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Zig_Zag_Railway.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: clear:right;\"><img alt=\"A historical view of the Zig Zag Railway line ...\" border=\"0\" class=\"zemanta-img-inserted\" height=\"302\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Zig_Zag_Railway.jpg/300px-Zig_Zag_Railway.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; border-color: initial; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-style: none; border-width: initial; font-size: 0.8em;\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption zemanta-img-attribution\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 300px;\">A historical view of the Zig Zag Railway line with top road on number 1 viaduct in the foreground and viaducts numbers 2 and 3 of middle road halfway down the valley. (Photo credit: <a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Zig_Zag_Railway.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a>)</td></tr></tbody></table><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/57650312@N05/7400007326/\" title=\"Zig Zag Railway\"><img alt=\"Zig Zag Railway by markfchristopher\" src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7241/7400007326_61e2b7985d.jpg\" /></a><br /><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/57650312@N05/7400007326/\">Zig Zag Railway</a>, a photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/57650312@N05/\">markfchristopher</a> on Flickr.<a href=\"http://www.westernadvocate.com.au/news/local/news/general/zig-zag-railways-last-run/2595552.aspx\">Another sad day.</a><br /><br />Why is it so hard to care about our heritage in Australia?<br /><br /><br /><br />This picture was taken a number of years ago at the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zig_Zag_Railway\">Zig Zag Railway at Lithgow</a> and we had a great adventure on the Wizard Express on Platform 3 3/4. So many volunteer hours to keep what is one of the big historical railway wonders of the world that is part of our history being shut down and ignored as usual.<br /><br /><br /> <a class=\"zemanta-pixie-a\" href=\"http://www.zemanta.com/?px\" title=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\"><img alt=\"Enhanced by Zemanta\" class=\"zemanta-pixie-img\" src=\"http://img.zemanta.com/zemified_e.png?x-id=4a424be6-0e7c-4589-a0f4-3a55a1ab939d\" style=\"border: none; float: right;\" /></a><img width=&apos;1&apos; height=&apos;1&apos; src=&apos;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/7998294428961863698-1504121322416275391?l=notreallyalibrarian-markwashere.blogspot.com&apos; alt=&apos;&apos; />',1347893890,NULL,NULL,'markwashere','http://www.blogger.com/profile/16895029067006588081','2012-06-19T18:15:00.001+10:00',NULL,'something found or shared',NULL,'<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container zemanta-img\" style=\"float: right; margin-right: 1em; text-align: right;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:1072_passing_Bottom_Points_Signal_Box_on_the_Lithgow_Zig_Zag_railway_line.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: clear:right;\"><img alt=\"1072 passing Bottom Points Signal Box on the L...\" border=\"0\" class=\"zemanta-img-inserted\" height=\"292\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/1072_passing_Bottom_Points_Signal_Box_on_the_Lithgow_Zig_Zag_railway_line.jpg/300px-1072_passing_Bottom_Points_Signal_Box_on_the_Lithgow_Zig_Zag_railway_line.jpg\" style=\"border: none; font-size: 0.8em;\" width=\"300\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption zemanta-img-attribution\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 300px;\">1072 passing Bottom Points Signal Box on the Lithgow Zig Zag railway line. (Photo credit: <a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:1072_passing_Bottom_Points_Signal_Box_on_the_Lithgow_Zig_Zag_railway_line.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a>)</td></tr></tbody></table><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container zemanta-img\" style=\"float: right; margin-right: 1em; text-align: right;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://commons.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Zig_Zag_Railway.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: clear:right;\"><img alt=\"A historical view of the Zig Zag Railway line ...\" border=\"0\" class=\"zemanta-img-inserted\" height=\"302\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Zig_Zag_Railway.jpg/300px-Zig_Zag_Railway.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; border-color: initial; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-style: none; border-width: initial; font-size: 0.8em;\" width=\"400\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class=\"tr-caption zemanta-img-attribution\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 300px;\">A historical view of the Zig Zag Railway line with top road on number 1 viaduct in the foreground and viaducts numbers 2 and 3 of middle road halfway down the valley. (Photo cre