aymaker said, &quot;As a designer this is a very different experience than building in Second Life.Â  Designing and building in a virtual world makes scale fluid, malleable, imaginative--I love megaprims!&quot; <p /> Plans are afoot to integrate a solar array installation along with a green roof. It will be a challenge to see how this all fits together. A virtual world offers an excellent way to simulate the proposals. As for the performance space itself, the imagination--again, is the limit. Complimenting the virtual aspects of place are the mixed media and events occurring hyper locally.Â  &quot;This intersection of imagined and constructed space, immersed within a locality that is mirrored through a wider media ecology is the dimension I am interested in&quot;, says Pausanius.<p /> We will stay tuned for late breaking developments--best of luck Pausanius!<p />Reported by Virtual Dude, Reactiongrid, Ontos2--somewhere in the cloud.<p /> <p>\n<a href=\"http://getfile2.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/nvdTG9Dip9trHp4eU3I5RnPKgyMInt8CaD1z0VtWtjwhLrZSTQPKhcOCUfSe/Dibden_Ontos2_001.png.scaled.1000.jpg\"><img alt=\"Dibden_ontos2_001\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://getfile1.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/fZLUPQKnZNDcODuTfwnYd5IQFgG3bBM0P5DdQrX3sgoiUhOg1mCJkoE0n2YX/Dibden_Ontos2_001.png.scaled.500.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://getfile7.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/RQaqHVQvDpZGujS76cOjTh3LENnlgjBE1ndamzLjpcbjNA1D5OA3mMZIabcx/Dibden_Ontos2_002.png.scaled.1000.jpg\"><img alt=\"Dibden_ontos2_002\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://getfile6.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/hlVpxXStWxmiPWVBYwLk3fV2VSylvFMh9FX1YEBXmdZwwKYxRkpha02gWzbp/Dibden_Ontos2_002.png.scaled.500.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://getfile3.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/CCLk3E8kUBiAk2KaONHZ1wnkJngegCtpoLcxUPOeOt82hggOHVzKOAGBolyJ/Dibden_Ontos2_003.png.scaled.1000.jpg\"><img alt=\"Dibden_ontos2_003\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://getfile2.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/w2QMLQs4lmWzUkKBAKSTphDGsiSZ7yGspCg0dpl5EpcIiH7aY9Lx252aXv8Q/Dibden_Ontos2_003.png.scaled.500.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://getfile9.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/XkIl9KRnv6U9VyBnMcg3aCgzp6EnvzETQo1ChawNiBI0Emy3d6WaYsNVH4TR/Dibden_Ontos2_004.png.scaled.1000.jpg\"><img alt=\"Dibden_ontos2_004\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://getfile8.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/mrZclv3fEl9w3OlNGvxJIWeBXX2yM3kZTtBWuKITyM5OZ2uj19666hQn12i0/Dibden_Ontos2_004.png.scaled.500.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://getfile4.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/1aBVfd7y0ABUaN1emr9h5dL2sngOclZbtljd4oJoM2NTmYDoSJ7HOk9hdVzB/Dibden_Ontos2_005.png.scaled.1000.jpg\"><img alt=\"Dibden_ontos2_005\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://getfile3.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/mciI7007K7WOukg2yVtuSaQp8a1V7heC9ErHR1U73JbUpVTIWGpA1GNzffjW/Dibden_Ontos2_005.png.scaled.500.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://getfile9.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/I2wD9jF1IvjFpCCqyFpnRers0IDWWvZ8e24PHfXDmU0DLAuTJgeReEosaboI/Dibden_Ontos2_006.png.scaled.1000.jpg\"><img alt=\"Dibden_ontos2_006\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://getfile8.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/6vBO5wfFieWT1TS3X4uoSWYLOQC8dE8yLxoOCmj3xoYQ3PJzm2T8BNmUgzLo/Dibden_Ontos2_006.png.scaled.500.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://getfile5.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/lWy9rI2dv0Udxs6eiXs2sQJAIWpqOjO8C7QpA53cnGTzU0NX84NSehkJJ4vF/Dibden_Ontos2_007.png.scaled.1000.jpg\"><img alt=\"Dibden_ontos2_007\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://getfile4.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/blogasaurus/wA839a0Cnbljmh6PqyjDTScscfGRbD83Hvap4zG5DNCqmDPnGviO4qVskMxy/Dibden_Ontos2_007.png.scaled.500.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://blogasaurus.posterous.com/construction-on-virtual-d