ULL,NULL,NULL,'Fri, 28 Sep 2012 03:11:13 +0200',NULL,'CDATA(0)',NULL,'<hr/><p><strong><a href=&apos;https://plus.google.com/109188864678491369963/posts/iMZaZ1PqMt4&apos; target=&apos;_blank&apos;>Original Post</a> from <a href=&apos;https://plus.google.com/109188864678491369963&apos; target=&apos;_blank&apos;>Darren Cannell</a>:</strong></p><p></p><p class=&apos;attachment video&apos;>\n										<a href=&apos;http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ax5cNlutAys&apos; target=&apos;_blank&apos;><img src=&apos;https://images0-focus-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?container=focus&gadget=a&resize_h=100&url=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FAx5cNlutAys%2Fhqdefault.jpg&apos; height=&apos;100&apos;/>What is 21st century education?</a>\n									</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,NULL),(747,0,0,'Second week of Twitter class discussions This week I added one more rule: \"Remember that during a...','text/html','https://plus.google.com/110117137800261731479/posts/cMhhNAfLWAQ','category',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,6,'Second week of Twitter class discussionsThis week I added one more rule: &quot;Remember that during a discussion, you comment on other peoples&#39; opinions. Do you agree with what they are saying? Let them know why. If you disagree with somebody, however, respectfully explain why you have a different opinion&quot;.This meant that replying to my question was not enough. They had to comment on each other&#39;s opinions.Did it work? I would say yes. Here&#39;s the evidence, and you can make up your own mind.<p class=&apos;attachment article&apos;>\n										<a href=&apos;http://storify.com/bernardotrejos/discussion-on-fear&apos; target=&apos;_blank&apos;>Discussion on fear</a>\n									</p><p class=&apos;attachment photo&apos;>\n										<a href=&apos;http://storify.com/bernardotrejos/discussion-on-fear&apos; target=&apos;_blank&apos;><img src=&apos;https://images0-focus-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?container=focus&gadget=a&resize_h=100&url=http%3A%2F%2Fstorify.com%2Fpublic%2Fimg%2Fdefault-thumb.gif&apos; height=&apos;100&apos;/> </a>\n									</p>',1348802763,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fri, 28 Sep 2012 02:30:22 +0200',NULL,'CDATA(0)',NULL,'Second week of Twitter class discussionsThis week I added one more rule: &quot;Remember that during a discussion, you comment on other peoples&#39; opinions. Do you agree with what they are saying? Let them know why. If you disagree with somebody, however, respectfully explain why you have a different opinion&quot;.This meant that replying to my question was not enough. They had to comment on each other&#39;s opinions.Did it work? I would say yes. Here&#39;s the evidence, and you can make up your own mind.<p class=&apos;attachment article&apos;>\n										<a href=&apos;http://storify.com/bernardotrejos/discussion-on-fear&apos; target=&apos;_blank&apos;>Discussion on fear</a>\n									</p><p class=&apos;attachment photo&apos;>\n										<a href=&apos;http://storify.com/bernardotrejos/discussion-on-fear&apos; target=&apos;_blank&apos;><img src=&apos;https://images0-focus-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?container=focus&gadget=a&resize_h=100&url=http%3A%2F%2Fstorify.com%2Fpublic%2Fimg%2Fdefault-thumb.gif&apos; height=&apos;100&apos;/> </a>\n									</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,NULL),(748,0,0,'RT @michaelweissca: RT @michaelweissca: Fully agree RT @gsiemens: Remix Manifesto is one the best intros to IP/content protection: http://t.co/Czv0y3Cu #oped12','twitter','http://twitter.com/dieGoerelebt/statuses/251527143664803840','edubloggers',NULL,NULL,342,'http://twitter.com/dieGoerelebt/statuses/251527143664803840',NULL,NULL,29,'RT @<a class=\" \" href=\"https://twitter.com/michaelweissca\">michaelweissca</a>: RT @<a class=\" \" href=\"https://twitter.com/michaelweissca\">michaelweissca</a>: Fully agree RT @<a class=\" \" href=\"https://t