w.diigo.com/user/dougpete/ipad\">ipad</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/iphone\">iphone</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/moviemaking\">moviemaking</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/film\">film</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/filming\">filming</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://k12blueprint.com\">K-12 Blueprint | Resources for planning and implementing technology initiatives</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">&#8220;Resources for planning and implementing technology initiatives&#8221;</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/technology\">technology</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/initiatives\">initiatives</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/edtech\">edtech</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/blueprint\">blueprint</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/planning\">planning</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/resources\">resources</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/education/k12/teach-elements.html\">IntelÂ® Teach Elements-Online Professional Development Courses</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">IntelÂ® Teach Elements-Online Professional Development Courses &#8211; http://t.co/dAjH19um</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/via:packrati.us\">via:packrati.us</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://yttm.tv/y/1988\">YTTM.tv &#8211; Pick a year, click refresh, and TRAVEL THROUGH TIME.</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">YouTube Time Machine</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/click\">click</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/travel\">travel</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/time\">time</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/youtube\">youtube</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://ipad.appfinders.com/teleprompter-apps-for-ipad/\">5 Cool Teleprompter Apps for iPad | iPad App Finders</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">&#8220;Some people love making fun of teleprompters and those who use them. But these tools can be quite helpful in improving your public speaking skills. They are handy for giving great speeches too. Teleprompters could be a bit costly. Thanks to these iPad apps, you can use your iPad as your teleprompter:&#8221;</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/ipad\">ipad</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/apps\">apps</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/teleprompter\">teleprompter</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://www.mp3grabber.net\">Free MP3 Grabber &#8211; search and grab mp3 from YouTube, Dailymotion, MySpace, vevo, imeem, last.fm and many other online resources for free</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">Paste video URL or Enter Keywords to Search MP3</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/mp3\">mp3</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/youtube\">youtube</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/audio\">audio</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/grabber\">grabber</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://kleinerin.visibli.com/share/bxdN6Y\">BabyLit Board BooksFudge Banana Swirl</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">Share classical literature with your little ones: http://t.co/eFsDcFBt</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/via:packrati.us\">via:packrati.us</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/literature\">literature</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/classical\">classical</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://makethedrop.ca/education\">Education | MAKETHEDROP.CA</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">FYI Teachers &#8211; OD presenters can come to your school for free to do classroom or assembly presentations Info: http://t. &#8230;</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/via:packrati.us\">via:packrati.us</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/blog-to-book-author/\">5 Ways to Go From Blogger to Published Book Author | Social Media Examiner</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">RT @2morrowknight: 5 Ways to Go From #Blogger to Published Book Author http://t.co/VcBTcwuuÂ #books</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/Blogger\">Blogger</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/via:packrati.us\">via:packrati.us</a>      <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/books\">books</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"https://foursquare.com/dougpete/badge/5064811ce4b0e1bb813d5f4b?ref=tw\">Doug&#8217;s Badges &#8211; Great Outdoors &#8211; foursquare</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">I just reached Level 4 of the &#8220;Great Outdoors&#8221; badge on @foursquare. I&apos;ve checked in at 15 different outdoor spots! http://t.co/C9nGg6q7</p>\n<p class=\"diigo-tags\">     tags:           <a href=\"http://www.diigo.com/user/dougpete/via:packrati.us\">via:packrati.us</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"diigo-link\">        <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2012/06/01/e-reading-trends/\">Do E-Reader Owners Read More Books? [INFOGRAPHIC]</a>   </p>\n<p class=\"diigo-description\">&#8220;U.S. consumers with an e-reader or tablet are more likely to read and buy books than those without an e-book compatible tech device,